1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:29,980
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:32,980
= Episode 27 =

20
00:01:52,420 --> 00:01:53,140
Your Majesty,

21
00:01:54,140 --> 00:01:56,660
should the lunch be set at your chamber,

22
00:01:56,660 --> 00:01:57,460
or…

23
00:02:01,740 --> 00:02:02,540
Huaiji,

24
00:02:05,500 --> 00:02:06,900
accompany me to the Hall of Peace.

25
00:02:26,700 --> 00:02:29,340
I’ve never worn this crown before.

26
00:02:31,700 --> 00:02:33,260
It’s not of the usual ceremonial style

27
00:02:33,300 --> 00:02:35,740
and too extravagant to be worn in everyday life.

28
00:02:37,900 --> 00:02:38,820
I’m afraid it would appear gaudy.

29
00:02:40,020 --> 00:02:41,140
But your charm is unpatrolled.

30
00:02:41,500 --> 00:02:42,940
Even when wearing simple things,
you would not appear bland.

31
00:02:43,380 --> 00:02:45,060
And when dressed up, you would not appear garish.

32
00:02:47,980 --> 00:02:48,780
Qiuhe,

33
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,340
do you know Zhang Maoze,

34
00:02:55,100 --> 00:02:55,860
from Imperial Office Bureau?

35
00:02:57,420 --> 00:02:59,060
The day before I was selected to work
in the palace,

36
00:02:59,460 --> 00:03:01,340
I was indeed summoned by Mr. Zhang

37
00:03:01,340 --> 00:03:02,460
and asked a few questions.

38
00:03:06,860 --> 00:03:07,900
That should be it.

39
00:03:10,420 --> 00:03:12,260
If no one had high hope on you,

40
00:03:12,660 --> 00:03:13,660
however talented you were,

41
00:03:14,620 --> 00:03:16,100
the Chief of Styling would not allow you to

42
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:17,460
skip being tutored by a master

43
00:03:17,460 --> 00:03:18,980
to directly serve a concubine.

44
00:03:23,140 --> 00:03:24,540
Madam Miao was right.

45
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:27,700
It was indeed a shame

46
00:03:27,700 --> 00:03:28,780
to confine you to this palace.

47
00:03:37,700 --> 00:03:39,740
You shall return to the Bureau of Clothing

48
00:03:40,980 --> 00:03:42,180
and resume your post as a stylist.

49
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:45,420
Even though you are smart and diligent,

50
00:03:46,620 --> 00:03:47,940
you are new to the palace.

51
00:03:50,180 --> 00:03:51,500
This is different from elsewhere.

52
00:03:52,020 --> 00:03:53,940
No wrongdoing would be tolerated here.

53
00:03:56,260 --> 00:03:57,540
Apart from designing hairstyles,

54
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,060
and making crowns and face accessories,

55
00:03:59,460 --> 00:04:01,420
you have much to learn from the master.

56
00:04:02,620 --> 00:04:05,420
It’s not necessarily a good thing to rise too fast.

57
00:04:09,020 --> 00:04:11,940
I will bear your teachings in mind.

58
00:04:13,980 --> 00:04:14,940
His Majesty has arrived.

59
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:24,860
Your Majesty.

60
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:28,140
Your Highness, you are so beautiful.

61
00:04:30,020 --> 00:04:30,820
Your Majesty.

62
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:37,980
All these years

63
00:04:38,900 --> 00:04:41,300
I have never seen you dressed up like this.

64
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,420
Xinhe also looks different

65
00:04:45,420 --> 00:04:46,500
from usual.

66
00:04:47,580 --> 00:04:50,300
Did you all

67
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,300
dress yourselves up behind my back?

68
00:04:51,620 --> 00:04:53,820
Had I not visited unannounced today,

69
00:04:54,020 --> 00:04:55,100
would I not have the luck to see you like this?

70
00:04:57,820 --> 00:04:58,740
It’s almost lunchtime.

71
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:00,980
Perhaps Your Majesty wouldn’t mind dining here.

72
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:05,340
Today, I have come to the Hall of Peace

73
00:05:05,340 --> 00:05:06,620
without prior notice.

74
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:07,580
I fear that my Empress

75
00:05:07,580 --> 00:05:09,220
would only serve me vegetables and tofu.

76
00:05:10,780 --> 00:05:12,820
- I would pay from my own pocket,
- Could you come with me?

77
00:05:12,820 --> 00:05:14,060
and have the kitchen prepare more dishes.

78
00:05:14,340 --> 00:05:16,700
I have to keep the integrity of the Empress.

79
00:05:21,020 --> 00:05:22,140
The other day, when we came back,

80
00:05:22,140 --> 00:05:24,260
did father punish you?

81
00:05:24,780 --> 00:05:25,660
My princess,

82
00:05:25,900 --> 00:05:28,020
apart from a pay reduction,
there was no other punishment.

83
00:05:28,180 --> 00:05:29,060
A pay reduction?

84
00:05:29,460 --> 00:05:31,540
Might you not have enough money to pay for food?

85
00:05:31,980 --> 00:05:33,020
That won’t happen, my princess.

86
00:05:33,900 --> 00:05:35,700
Would you still be able to afford candies?

87
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:37,500
Don’t worry, my princess.

88
00:05:37,620 --> 00:05:38,460
In the palace,

89
00:05:38,460 --> 00:05:40,260
we won’t starve without money.

90
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:41,580
Besides,

91
00:05:41,580 --> 00:05:43,500
we don’t often get to spend money.

92
00:05:43,820 --> 00:05:44,940
His Majesty has been kind.

93
00:05:45,100 --> 00:05:47,820
A three-month pay reduction
was a light punishment indeed.

94
00:05:48,420 --> 00:05:50,060
I’m at ease then.

95
00:05:50,660 --> 00:05:51,780
Thank you for your consideration.

96
00:05:52,420 --> 00:05:54,140
Why are you so polite?

97
00:05:54,260 --> 00:05:56,260
It’s not that you haven’t helped me.

98
00:05:56,940 --> 00:05:58,420
I am not like you.

99
00:05:58,740 --> 00:06:00,020
I don’t keep thanking people.

100
00:06:00,860 --> 00:06:02,260
If you wish to thank me,

101
00:06:02,260 --> 00:06:04,820
why not tell me who Madam Ban is,

102
00:06:04,820 --> 00:06:06,180
and who Zhao Feiyan is.

103
00:06:06,820 --> 00:06:08,420
Were they not among the esteemed ladies

104
00:06:08,420 --> 00:06:09,380
that you were told stories about?

105
00:06:09,500 --> 00:06:10,380
No.

106
00:06:10,860 --> 00:06:13,860
I asked mother, but she knew nothing about them.

107
00:06:13,860 --> 00:06:15,340
I also asked Her Highness.

108
00:06:15,340 --> 00:06:18,060
But she said that I would not

109
00:06:18,060 --> 00:06:20,900
experience anything like Madam Ban did.

110
00:06:20,980 --> 00:06:23,020
So there was no need for me to learn about her.

111
00:06:23,420 --> 00:06:25,300
At last, I went to ask father.

112
00:06:25,580 --> 00:06:27,420
Father asked me,

113
00:06:27,700 --> 00:06:30,220
“Did you remember

114
00:06:30,500 --> 00:06:33,580
the story I told you yesterday

115
00:06:33,580 --> 00:06:35,020
about the Elder Princess of Wei?

116
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:38,060
Write it down for me”.

117
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:40,940
The Elder Princess of Wei

118
00:06:40,940 --> 00:06:42,260
is His Majesty’s aunt.

119
00:06:42,500 --> 00:06:43,620
She is kind and elegant.

120
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:45,580
She is a role model for the ladies of our country.

121
00:06:45,700 --> 00:06:48,980
I have heard many stories

122
00:06:49,100 --> 00:06:51,180
about how filial, virtuous,

123
00:06:51,380 --> 00:06:52,500
sensible and kind she is.

124
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:55,500
How much did you write?

125
00:06:56,020 --> 00:06:57,620
A few words.

126
00:06:58,180 --> 00:06:59,220
A few words?

127
00:07:00,100 --> 00:07:02,220
Even though I only wrote a few words,

128
00:07:02,220 --> 00:07:05,660
no one could say that what I wrote was inaccurate.

129
00:07:06,820 --> 00:07:10,460
You could summarize the stories

130
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:12,060
of the Elder Princess in a few words?

131
00:07:12,540 --> 00:07:13,780
I am benighted.

132
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:15,540
I am curious how you

133
00:07:15,860 --> 00:07:17,340
summarized the virtues of the Elder Princess

134
00:07:17,340 --> 00:07:19,140
in a few words.

135
00:07:19,700 --> 00:07:21,140
Please enlighten me.

136
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:22,860
What I wrote was

137
00:07:23,180 --> 00:07:25,820
that the Elder Princess of Wei is good,

138
00:07:26,020 --> 00:07:28,420
quite good, very good.

139
00:07:35,900 --> 00:07:36,740
That kid.

140
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:38,860
We should teach her manners.

141
00:07:40,500 --> 00:07:41,780
Huirou is smart and sensible.

142
00:07:41,780 --> 00:07:43,100
She’s always well-mannered in public.

143
00:07:43,380 --> 00:07:44,460
She is just outgoing.

144
00:07:44,620 --> 00:07:45,860
There is nothing wrong with that.

145
00:07:46,980 --> 00:07:48,620
There is indeed nothing wrong with being outgoing.

146
00:07:49,220 --> 00:07:50,420
But the kid is quite stubborn.

147
00:07:50,940 --> 00:07:52,140
And now Your Majesty and Your Highness

148
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:53,500
are both spoiling her.

149
00:07:53,780 --> 00:07:55,460
I want to spoil her my whole life

150
00:07:55,900 --> 00:07:57,580
so that she can always be this happy

151
00:07:57,980 --> 00:07:59,100
and laugh out loud like this.

152
00:08:04,020 --> 00:08:06,860
I will sure find her a husband

153
00:08:06,860 --> 00:08:08,580
who loves her deeply.

154
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:10,140
Other things don’t matter,

155
00:08:11,460 --> 00:08:14,020
but he must enable her to be like this

156
00:08:14,980 --> 00:08:16,460
and not let her go through any grievance.

157
00:08:24,140 --> 00:08:27,060
= The Hall of Peace =

158
00:08:45,940 --> 00:08:46,660
Huaiji.

159
00:08:48,020 --> 00:08:49,220
See Fu Bi at once

160
00:08:49,380 --> 00:08:50,220
and tell him

161
00:08:50,860 --> 00:08:51,980
to prepare to set off for Liao.

162
00:08:53,220 --> 00:08:55,020
He will have to go there himself.

163
00:08:56,500 --> 00:08:57,780
Ask him to tell the Emperor of Liao

164
00:08:58,220 --> 00:08:59,580
that Liao and Song have long been allies.

165
00:09:00,220 --> 00:09:01,260
The two nations are as close as brothers.

166
00:09:02,860 --> 00:09:04,780
Now Liao shall be on Song’s side,

167
00:09:05,100 --> 00:09:06,620
and should not trade with Yuanhao.

168
00:09:08,580 --> 00:09:10,580
As for the marriage proposal,

169
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:12,380
I do not think it’s wise.

170
00:09:14,220 --> 00:09:15,780
It is more likely for a married couple

171
00:09:15,780 --> 00:09:17,060
to be at odds with each other than brothers.

172
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:20,260
I believe that a marriage

173
00:09:20,260 --> 00:09:21,540
is not as simple, quick

174
00:09:22,580 --> 00:09:24,020
and productive

175
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,500
as financial aid.

176
00:09:27,100 --> 00:09:27,820
Yes.

177
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:38,780
During 1038 to 1040 A.D.,

178
00:09:39,020 --> 00:09:41,700
Song Qi was the first to point out the issue
of the “three excesses”.

179
00:09:42,580 --> 00:09:44,540
That is, the excesses of bureaucrats,
soldiers and monks.

180
00:09:45,500 --> 00:09:49,060
Even though the income from crop production,
mineral products and trade

181
00:09:49,500 --> 00:09:51,380
is each a few times more than
that in Han and Tang Dynasties.

182
00:09:51,580 --> 00:09:52,700
However, due to the three excesses,

183
00:09:52,700 --> 00:09:54,580
the nation is seeing a budget deficit.

184
00:09:56,060 --> 00:09:57,020
In my opinion,

185
00:09:57,420 --> 00:09:59,780
the three excesses not only cost
an exorbitant amount of money,

186
00:10:00,580 --> 00:10:02,180
but are also the cause
of the government’s low efficiency

187
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:04,260
and the military’s lackluster performance.

188
00:10:07,140 --> 00:10:10,140
= Lv Yijian, courtesy name Tanfu =
= Yan Shu, courtesy name Tongshu =

189
00:10:17,180 --> 00:10:18,660
I asked the ministries to submit

190
00:10:19,860 --> 00:10:21,180
a report on expenses of all

191
00:10:21,500 --> 00:10:23,100
Imperial Guards, Garrison Troops,

192
00:10:23,420 --> 00:10:24,500
wartime army provisions

193
00:10:24,500 --> 00:10:25,900
and post-war compensation in Shaanxi.

194
00:10:26,380 --> 00:10:28,860
First, it was a month of no reply.

195
00:10:29,340 --> 00:10:31,780
Then the Ministry of Finance pushed the matter
to the Ministry of Revenue.

196
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,860
The Ministry of Revenue submitted
a lengthy proposal

197
00:10:34,860 --> 00:10:36,100
claiming it was the responsibility
of the Ministry of Finance.

198
00:10:36,580 --> 00:10:37,460
Two more months later,

199
00:10:37,820 --> 00:10:38,780
I still see no word

200
00:10:38,900 --> 00:10:40,260
on what I wanted to know.

201
00:10:40,580 --> 00:10:41,340
What was presented to me

202
00:10:41,660 --> 00:10:43,540
were reports from the Ministries of Finance,
Revenue, War,

203
00:10:43,540 --> 00:10:44,620
and even Works,

204
00:10:44,780 --> 00:10:46,500
accusing each other of low efficiency.

205
00:10:49,460 --> 00:10:52,580
During the reign of the late Emperor,

206
00:10:52,780 --> 00:10:54,700
there were almost ten thousand officials.

207
00:10:55,380 --> 00:10:56,180
Now,

208
00:10:56,740 --> 00:10:59,060
that number has risen to over fifteen thousand.

209
00:10:59,940 --> 00:11:01,500
The ministries’ responsibilities overlap
with each other,

210
00:11:02,020 --> 00:11:04,700
while multiple people are assigned
to the same post.

211
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:05,900
When conducting duties,

212
00:11:06,300 --> 00:11:08,460
sometimes officials shirk responsibilities
to others,

213
00:11:08,860 --> 00:11:11,340
and sometimes matters get held up

214
00:11:11,340 --> 00:11:13,980
due to disagreements.

215
00:11:14,580 --> 00:11:15,500
In all,

216
00:11:16,180 --> 00:11:19,220
the excess of officials is indeed

217
00:11:19,420 --> 00:11:21,820
the cause of high expenses and low efficiency.

218
00:11:25,700 --> 00:11:26,860
Your Majesty,

219
00:11:27,780 --> 00:11:30,420
are you planning to change the methods
installed by your ancestors?

220
00:11:39,540 --> 00:11:42,620
I am old

221
00:11:43,100 --> 00:11:44,860
and do not have much time left in my life.

222
00:11:45,460 --> 00:11:47,980
Therefore, I dare not lie

223
00:11:48,420 --> 00:11:49,500
or withhold information from Your Majesty.

224
00:11:50,420 --> 00:11:51,940
When Song was first established,

225
00:11:52,460 --> 00:11:54,620
the Founding Father took caution of

226
00:11:54,620 --> 00:11:57,900
local powers taking central governance
in Mid-Tang Dynasty

227
00:11:58,420 --> 00:12:00,900
and acknowledged the importance
of restricting local powers.

228
00:12:01,380 --> 00:12:03,340
However, if power was directly taken from them,

229
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:06,340
it could create revolt and hatred.

230
00:12:07,460 --> 00:12:09,820
After lengthy consideration, the Founding Father

231
00:12:10,020 --> 00:12:13,060
devised the method of lengthening the procedure

232
00:12:13,220 --> 00:12:15,940
and creating more governmental
posts for checks and balances.

233
00:12:16,660 --> 00:12:17,500
In this way,

234
00:12:17,540 --> 00:12:19,660
expenses were added,

235
00:12:20,020 --> 00:12:21,580
but the possibility

236
00:12:21,580 --> 00:12:23,380
of local powers threatening the central government

237
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:26,620
was extirpated.

238
00:12:27,420 --> 00:12:29,020
As for the pros and cons,

239
00:12:30,620 --> 00:12:32,580
I ask for deliberations from Your Majesty.

240
00:12:39,540 --> 00:12:40,580
Prime Minister Lv, please sit down.

241
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:46,940
The same applies to the excess of soldiers.

242
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:50,020
The Founding Father decreed that

243
00:12:50,500 --> 00:12:53,420
keeping the military would benefit generations
to come.

244
00:12:54,300 --> 00:12:56,180
When years of famine hit,

245
00:12:56,900 --> 00:12:59,620
peasants revolt, but not soldiers.

246
00:13:00,620 --> 00:13:03,260
Therefore, whenever famine hits,

247
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:05,900
the government will conscript peasants
who were affected

248
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:07,860
to prevent them

249
00:13:08,460 --> 00:13:10,380
from taking extreme measures.

250
00:13:31,620 --> 00:13:32,620
What Prime Minister Lv has said

251
00:13:33,020 --> 00:13:34,420
represents seasoned strategies
for managing the nation.

252
00:13:35,340 --> 00:13:36,460
The opinions of the Founding Father

253
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:37,860
were indeed ingenious.

254
00:13:38,820 --> 00:13:39,780
But nowadays,

255
00:13:40,820 --> 00:13:43,180
the number of bureaucrats is twice
that of the Founding Father’s time,

256
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:45,300
while the number of the Imperial Guards
is more than three times.

257
00:13:46,220 --> 00:13:47,780
Now, we are experiencing a lot more drawbacks

258
00:13:47,980 --> 00:13:50,740
of the excess of bureaucrats
and soldiers than in previous regimes.

259
00:13:50,940 --> 00:13:53,180
This is due to my wrongdoings.

260
00:13:53,780 --> 00:13:54,460
We shall make changes.

261
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:57,460
This is to change my own wrongdoings,

262
00:13:58,300 --> 00:14:00,220
not to change the methods installed
by my ancestors.

263
00:14:03,220 --> 00:14:04,220
All right.

264
00:14:05,900 --> 00:14:10,180
Your majesty, you have heard enough of my old soul.

265
00:14:11,420 --> 00:14:12,420
I shall take my leave.

266
00:14:13,980 --> 00:14:14,940
I shall take my leave.

267
00:14:15,500 --> 00:14:17,660
Liaozi, arrange a sedan chair
for Prime Minister Lv.

268
00:14:18,380 --> 00:14:19,100
Yes.

269
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:29,900
He does not have the heart to send Huirou to Liao.

270
00:14:30,540 --> 00:14:31,900
But Chuyue was cursed to death.

271
00:14:31,900 --> 00:14:33,100
Yet he asks nothing of it.

272
00:14:35,740 --> 00:14:37,060
Does he think that I am a pet

273
00:14:37,500 --> 00:14:38,540
that I could be consoled by these?

274
00:14:39,380 --> 00:14:40,860
You have lost your poise again.

275
00:14:42,260 --> 00:14:43,660
Who is going to benefit

276
00:14:43,660 --> 00:14:44,620
if you keep being angry with His Majesty?

277
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:47,500
Do not throw these anymore.

278
00:14:50,500 --> 00:14:51,660
I cannot forget about Chuyue.

279
00:14:57,100 --> 00:14:59,100
Then you should take better care of yourself.

280
00:15:00,340 --> 00:15:01,340
Restore your health

281
00:15:02,420 --> 00:15:03,060
so that

282
00:15:03,060 --> 00:15:04,780
you can give birth to a strong and healthy son.

283
00:15:04,980 --> 00:15:06,180
Considering how His Majesty adores you,

284
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:07,220
would the officials

285
00:15:07,260 --> 00:15:08,620
pander to the Empress

286
00:15:08,620 --> 00:15:09,700
or Madam Miao?

287
00:15:10,020 --> 00:15:10,980
They could try.

288
00:15:17,580 --> 00:15:18,220
Right.

289
00:15:18,860 --> 00:15:19,940
There have been rumors

290
00:15:20,100 --> 00:15:21,900
about what is going on in the household of Mr. Xia.

291
00:15:22,620 --> 00:15:23,660
It is rumored that Mrs. Xia

292
00:15:23,900 --> 00:15:25,700
has been complaining to people
about him being corrupted and adulterous.

293
00:15:26,100 --> 00:15:27,180
She was so upset

294
00:15:27,620 --> 00:15:28,820
that she listed each of

295
00:15:29,140 --> 00:15:30,180
his wrongdoings

296
00:15:30,620 --> 00:15:31,700
and submitted to the government.

297
00:15:33,340 --> 00:15:34,020
Nowadays,

298
00:15:34,300 --> 00:15:36,220
Mr. Xia’s mother and his mother-in-law

299
00:15:36,700 --> 00:15:38,260
are accusing each other

300
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:39,780
in the gathering of ladies

301
00:15:39,860 --> 00:15:40,980
of not educating their children well.

302
00:15:43,140 --> 00:15:43,940
Also,

303
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:47,420
I have selected some jewelry and fabric

304
00:15:47,700 --> 00:15:48,820
as regular rewards.

305
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,460
I will find an opportunity

306
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:52,540
to give them to

307
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:53,500
eunuchs and stewardesses with ranks.

308
00:15:57,140 --> 00:15:58,340
Do what you see fit, aunt.

309
00:16:02,540 --> 00:16:06,540
However, that Chief Li of Styling

310
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:08,220
is always thinking about

311
00:16:08,220 --> 00:16:09,500
how to seduce His Majesty.

312
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:11,140
Is it possible to bribe her?

313
00:16:12,300 --> 00:16:14,020
It would be good enough if the people

314
00:16:14,340 --> 00:16:15,260
who spend much time around His Majesty

315
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,580
do not spread rumors about us.

316
00:16:16,900 --> 00:16:17,700
What’s more,

317
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:19,340
however high their ranks are,

318
00:16:19,740 --> 00:16:22,660
they still have to depend

319
00:16:22,820 --> 00:16:23,940
on concubines who are in favor.

320
00:16:26,420 --> 00:16:27,100
By the way,

321
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:29,220
I have prepared specially for your uncle

322
00:16:29,220 --> 00:16:30,340
a jade ornament,

323
00:16:30,340 --> 00:16:31,620
and have Yang Huaimin

324
00:16:31,900 --> 00:16:33,380
find him a few great inkstones.

325
00:16:34,620 --> 00:16:35,300
Back in the days,

326
00:16:36,340 --> 00:16:38,020
when I asked for his help with my mother,

327
00:16:38,740 --> 00:16:40,100
he was afraid of his wife and dared not help us.

328
00:16:41,020 --> 00:16:43,540
Now I have His Majesty’s favor,

329
00:16:43,540 --> 00:16:44,700
he is sucking up to me.

330
00:16:47,300 --> 00:16:50,020
He has good reasons to get on good terms with you.

331
00:16:50,580 --> 00:16:51,540
However, you should

332
00:16:52,100 --> 00:16:53,140
have some people on your side

333
00:16:53,620 --> 00:16:54,540
in the government

334
00:16:54,540 --> 00:16:55,900
to watch out for you.

335
00:16:57,500 --> 00:17:00,100
He got appointed after passing the exam.

336
00:17:00,540 --> 00:17:03,380
Your kin is always more reliable than others.

337
00:17:05,100 --> 00:17:06,260
I don’t think so about uncle.

338
00:17:07,100 --> 00:17:07,980
I do not want to

339
00:17:08,060 --> 00:17:09,140
let his wife get away with it.

340
00:17:10,980 --> 00:17:12,220
I know very well

341
00:17:12,380 --> 00:17:13,500
what Lv Yijian wanted to express.

342
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:15,620
But upon close scrutiny of various

343
00:17:16,380 --> 00:17:17,900
revenue and expenses in the government and

344
00:17:18,460 --> 00:17:20,740
after experiencing two years’ of military action.

345
00:17:21,100 --> 00:17:22,460
Just one major case of Liu Ping,

346
00:17:23,180 --> 00:17:25,980
has exposed how the bureaucracy works
in local administrations.

347
00:17:26,260 --> 00:17:27,340
I cannot live with

348
00:17:27,580 --> 00:17:28,860
the damages of the three excesses anymore.

349
00:17:28,860 --> 00:17:29,820
Things have to change.

350
00:17:30,540 --> 00:17:33,540
Even if it was a cure for the symptoms

351
00:17:34,100 --> 00:17:35,780
but not the illness,

352
00:17:36,380 --> 00:17:38,060
a radical medication would have to be prescribed

353
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:40,140
and keep the excesses at bay.

354
00:17:41,380 --> 00:17:43,180
Who do Your Majesty have in mind?

355
00:17:45,540 --> 00:17:47,220
When it comes to making changes,

356
00:17:47,860 --> 00:17:50,620
it would involve many people’s interests.

357
00:17:51,260 --> 00:17:52,340
The person leading the initiative

358
00:17:52,580 --> 00:17:55,500
cannot afford any flaws in his morals.

359
00:17:55,860 --> 00:17:57,580
Otherwise, others would use it as a target

360
00:17:57,820 --> 00:17:58,820
and make a scene out of it.

361
00:17:58,900 --> 00:18:00,020
It would compromise the greater good due
to private interests.

362
00:18:02,140 --> 00:18:04,780
When it comes to the person who has no wrongdoings,

363
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:06,220
who has immaculate morals,

364
00:18:06,220 --> 00:18:07,380
who serves the public without any corruption,

365
00:18:08,420 --> 00:18:11,180
there is no one but Fan Zhongyan.

366
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:13,780
There indeed is no other better candidate.

367
00:18:15,180 --> 00:18:18,020
Fu Bi’s negotiations with Liao are going smoothly.

368
00:18:19,140 --> 00:18:20,180
Liao’s emperor has agreed

369
00:18:20,380 --> 00:18:22,540
to put pressure on ending trade with Yuanhao

370
00:18:22,700 --> 00:18:24,980
in exchange for one hundred thousand silver taels.

371
00:18:25,780 --> 00:18:27,540
Once Yuanhao cannot trade with Liao anymore,

372
00:18:27,980 --> 00:18:30,940
Xia’s various states would not be able
to exchange fur and rock salt

373
00:18:30,940 --> 00:18:32,220
for their life necessities.

374
00:18:32,980 --> 00:18:33,900
By next year at the latest,

375
00:18:34,860 --> 00:18:37,020
the border at Shaanxi would restore its peace

376
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:37,980
and reopen its markets.

377
00:18:37,980 --> 00:18:40,340
Then we can focus on tacking the excess problem.

378
00:18:44,620 --> 00:18:45,460
If Your Majesty

379
00:18:45,460 --> 00:18:47,180
could tackle the problem of the three excesses,

380
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:48,780
the finances would be replete

381
00:18:49,220 --> 00:18:51,420
and the society would thrive like the golden days
of the Han Dynasty.

382
00:18:53,900 --> 00:18:55,820
Could my son be like Emperor Wu of Han

383
00:18:56,180 --> 00:18:58,780
and one day expand the borders of our nation?

384
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:02,300
Mencius said that

385
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:04,740
people in the world look forward to emperors

386
00:19:04,980 --> 00:19:06,340
who do not like killing or wars.

387
00:19:06,820 --> 00:19:07,940
If the emperor is indeed kind,

388
00:19:07,980 --> 00:19:10,820
people of the world would stand by his side

389
00:19:10,820 --> 00:19:11,980
and support the kind emperor.

390
00:19:13,380 --> 00:19:16,180
Unfortunately, that is just the scholar’s dream.

391
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:17,980
However, over the past few decades,

392
00:19:18,340 --> 00:19:21,100
Liao has transformed from a culture in favor of war

393
00:19:21,380 --> 00:19:22,540
to learn about our customs

394
00:19:22,860 --> 00:19:24,580
and get to love farming and a peaceful life.

395
00:19:24,580 --> 00:19:25,580
That has made me feel that

396
00:19:26,540 --> 00:19:27,460
if one day

397
00:19:27,780 --> 00:19:29,420
the delicacies and rich wine,

398
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:30,460
and the exquisite silk of our nation

399
00:19:30,900 --> 00:19:32,580
could bring the nations around us
who are in favor of brute forces

400
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:34,500
off the horsebacks and make them never
want to get back on it

401
00:19:34,900 --> 00:19:36,540
without them realizing it,

402
00:19:38,180 --> 00:19:41,220
then eternal peace would be installed.

403
00:19:46,220 --> 00:19:47,380
Huirou has mentioned several times to me

404
00:19:48,060 --> 00:19:49,940
that she wished to learn drawing birds.

405
00:19:50,660 --> 00:19:51,780
You shall go to the Imperial Art Institute

406
00:19:51,780 --> 00:19:53,220
and ask the painter in duty

407
00:19:53,380 --> 00:19:55,460
to select a few paintings of flowers
and birds for Huirou to review

408
00:19:56,060 --> 00:19:57,180
and see what she likes.

409
00:19:59,580 --> 00:20:00,300
How about this?

410
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:02,500
You fetch the paintings from the Institute

411
00:20:02,660 --> 00:20:03,700
and deliver them to the Hall of Peace

412
00:20:03,700 --> 00:20:04,860
and present them to Empress first

413
00:20:05,340 --> 00:20:06,260
and have her select the paintings for Huirou.

414
00:20:16,980 --> 00:20:18,020
There is a rumor

415
00:20:19,340 --> 00:20:20,460
that I should not be asking about.

416
00:20:21,140 --> 00:20:21,980
However,

417
00:20:22,420 --> 00:20:23,900
the ladies in the place

418
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:24,780
are all talking about it nowadays.

419
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:27,980
What is going on

420
00:20:27,980 --> 00:20:29,100
with Xia Song’s wife?

421
00:20:29,660 --> 00:20:32,340
She has written a petition exposing
her husband’s corruption.

422
00:20:33,260 --> 00:20:33,940
This matter…

423
00:20:34,580 --> 00:20:36,620
I don’t know the ins and outs of this matter.

424
00:20:37,340 --> 00:20:40,740
It is said that the alleged corruption
in the petition

425
00:20:41,380 --> 00:20:45,020
is groundless.

426
00:20:45,860 --> 00:20:47,780
It was due to the jealous nature of women.

427
00:20:48,260 --> 00:20:49,380
Mrs. Xia is

428
00:20:50,420 --> 00:20:52,380
particularly narrow-minded and brute.

429
00:20:52,860 --> 00:20:54,220
That’s why things have come to the way they are.

430
00:20:59,620 --> 00:21:01,100
In terms of rewards issued out,

431
00:21:01,460 --> 00:21:03,140
there was only the case of

432
00:21:03,580 --> 00:21:05,060
rewards issued to the monks

433
00:21:05,140 --> 00:21:06,220
at the funeral of Princess Anshou

434
00:21:06,540 --> 00:21:08,380
which exceeded the established standards
in the palace.

435
00:21:08,900 --> 00:21:09,660
It was slightly over.

436
00:21:13,700 --> 00:21:14,980
Princess Anshou died young.

437
00:21:15,660 --> 00:21:17,140
His Majesty, as her father,

438
00:21:17,140 --> 00:21:18,100
couldn’t save his daughter.

439
00:21:19,340 --> 00:21:21,060
He couldn’t be seen cry for her.

440
00:21:21,900 --> 00:21:22,860
All this pain,

441
00:21:23,580 --> 00:21:25,020
he could only let out

442
00:21:25,180 --> 00:21:27,020
by giving her

443
00:21:27,540 --> 00:21:28,860
an extra big funeral.

444
00:21:29,540 --> 00:21:30,540
I understand.

445
00:21:31,860 --> 00:21:34,420
I also reminded the eunuch on duty back then

446
00:21:34,660 --> 00:21:35,580
not to speak of this

447
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:37,780
and did not talk about this with His Majesty.

448
00:21:43,060 --> 00:21:46,340
If there is nothing else
that Your Highness need me on,

449
00:21:47,580 --> 00:21:48,780
I shall leave.

450
00:21:54,060 --> 00:21:54,980
Pingfu.

451
00:21:57,740 --> 00:21:59,900
You are the eunuch His Majesty trusts the most

452
00:22:01,140 --> 00:22:03,300
and also one of the smartest,

453
00:22:03,300 --> 00:22:05,220
most capable staff in the palace.

454
00:22:09,380 --> 00:22:10,780
Since I came to the palace,

455
00:22:12,060 --> 00:22:14,020
you have helped me much.

456
00:22:14,100 --> 00:22:15,620
I am extremely grateful, but…

457
00:22:15,860 --> 00:22:16,660
Your Highness.

458
00:22:17,820 --> 00:22:19,220
Everything I have done

459
00:22:19,740 --> 00:22:21,900
is what I believe I should

460
00:22:22,140 --> 00:22:23,180
and must do.

461
00:22:24,740 --> 00:22:26,180
It is where my responsibilities lie
as a servant for His Majesty.

462
00:22:27,860 --> 00:22:29,780
Including personally attending
to Qiuhe’s promotion?

463
00:22:34,060 --> 00:22:36,140
Qiuhe’s qualities and credentials,

464
00:22:36,540 --> 00:22:37,460
as well as her capabilities,

465
00:22:38,020 --> 00:22:39,820
would qualify her for any promotion.

466
00:22:44,020 --> 00:22:45,900
It seems that I aasked her to return
to the Bureau of Clothing,

467
00:22:46,540 --> 00:22:47,500
which impeded her growth.

468
00:22:49,540 --> 00:22:52,140
Your Highness, you have your way of making
judgments and decisions.

469
00:22:53,060 --> 00:22:54,820
I do not know your thoughts

470
00:22:55,460 --> 00:22:57,700
and have never probed or asked
about them in advance.

471
00:22:58,420 --> 00:22:59,500
What I have done

472
00:22:59,940 --> 00:23:01,900
was merely based on my principles.

473
00:23:02,220 --> 00:23:04,540
I was merely doing what I thought I should do.

474
00:23:06,620 --> 00:23:07,700
Your decisions

475
00:23:07,860 --> 00:23:09,420
are naturally wiser than mine.

476
00:23:10,140 --> 00:23:12,820
Therefore, what Your Highness has decreed,

477
00:23:13,260 --> 00:23:14,580
I shall obey.

478
00:23:21,060 --> 00:23:21,900
Pingfu.

479
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:29,700
I know about your thoughts.

480
00:23:30,820 --> 00:23:31,940
I do not wish to quote

481
00:23:31,940 --> 00:23:33,460
the sayings of scholars.

482
00:23:35,260 --> 00:23:36,420
However, I believe you are also aware

483
00:23:38,540 --> 00:23:40,260
that what I want in my heart

484
00:23:41,260 --> 00:23:43,780
cannot be obtained by schemes.

485
00:23:45,140 --> 00:23:46,020
Why should we…

486
00:23:47,020 --> 00:23:48,260
I am humbled to be referred

487
00:23:50,700 --> 00:23:53,780
to as belonging to the same group as you.

488
00:23:56,820 --> 00:23:58,380
His Majesty and you

489
00:23:59,140 --> 00:24:00,180
are the purest, wisest people

490
00:24:00,300 --> 00:24:02,420
in this world.

491
00:24:02,940 --> 00:24:03,820
In terms of me,

492
00:24:04,460 --> 00:24:05,460
whether it’s attending to

493
00:24:05,460 --> 00:24:06,980
affairs in the palace on behalf of His Majesty

494
00:24:08,100 --> 00:24:09,420
or doing things that I consider appropriate

495
00:24:10,260 --> 00:24:11,980
for you,

496
00:24:14,060 --> 00:24:15,420
these are what I consider

497
00:24:18,500 --> 00:24:20,220
to be my own responsibilities
as a servant for the royalty.

498
00:24:21,460 --> 00:24:23,100
If His Majesty or you

499
00:24:23,620 --> 00:24:25,060
think that I have crossed the line

500
00:24:25,540 --> 00:24:26,500
and punished me,

501
00:24:27,980 --> 00:24:29,540
I would have no complaints.

502
00:24:33,460 --> 00:24:34,340
Your Highness.

503
00:24:36,580 --> 00:24:37,260
Your Highness.

504
00:24:37,620 --> 00:24:38,540
His Majesty has asked Huaiji

505
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:40,020
to bring some paintings of flowers and birds over

506
00:24:40,460 --> 00:24:42,500
and wishes you to select some for Princess Fukang.

507
00:24:46,540 --> 00:24:48,540
Your Majesty, you showed up all of a sudden

508
00:24:49,060 --> 00:24:50,860
with no prior notice.

509
00:24:53,100 --> 00:24:54,300
I have not been well-prepared

510
00:24:54,300 --> 00:24:55,700
and can only make you these noodles.

511
00:24:58,900 --> 00:24:59,820
You should take some rest

512
00:24:59,820 --> 00:25:00,820
and have the servants do these.

513
00:25:02,100 --> 00:25:03,660
It is rare for you to visit.

514
00:25:03,980 --> 00:25:05,500
I don’t want unnecessary people

515
00:25:05,500 --> 00:25:06,580
to get in the way.

516
00:25:08,140 --> 00:25:09,900
Wasn’t I here three days ago?

517
00:25:12,140 --> 00:25:12,860
Three days ago,

518
00:25:12,860 --> 00:25:14,340
you only stayed for an hour.

519
00:25:19,060 --> 00:25:20,860
Moreover, it is not enough to see you
once every three days.

520
00:25:25,340 --> 00:25:26,700
You are pregnant.

521
00:25:28,020 --> 00:25:28,860
You cannot exert yourself.

522
00:25:29,220 --> 00:25:30,460
Just talk with me.

523
00:25:32,860 --> 00:25:36,100
I don’t feel any discomfort this time.

524
00:25:37,420 --> 00:25:40,820
Chuyue must be looking out for me

525
00:25:41,940 --> 00:25:43,180
and her brothers and sisters in heaven.

526
00:25:46,220 --> 00:25:47,660
I hope this time everything will go smoothly.

527
00:25:48,260 --> 00:25:49,580
It doesn’t matter if it’s a boy or a girl

528
00:25:50,620 --> 00:25:51,820
as long as it is healthy.

529
00:26:12,940 --> 00:26:14,620
It was your idea to include these paintings
by Cui Bai

530
00:26:15,460 --> 00:26:17,380
in the selection, wasn’t it?

531
00:26:17,860 --> 00:26:19,100
It was true that the painter on duty

532
00:26:19,620 --> 00:26:21,220
did not pick these paintings.

533
00:26:22,220 --> 00:26:25,060
I acted recklessly.
I am willing to take your punishments.

534
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:27,620
Answer me first.

535
00:26:28,380 --> 00:26:30,060
Why did you choose

536
00:26:30,060 --> 00:26:31,020
these paintings by Cui Bai?

537
00:26:38,220 --> 00:26:39,460
Take this one for example.

538
00:26:39,780 --> 00:26:41,340
Tell me what you see in it.

539
00:26:48,860 --> 00:26:51,540
Pingfu, what do you think of the painting?

540
00:26:53,740 --> 00:26:56,300
The egret in the painting is quite vivid
in its poses,

541
00:26:56,620 --> 00:26:57,900
and the plumage seems soft and thick,

542
00:26:58,220 --> 00:26:59,660
as if you could touch it.

543
00:27:00,060 --> 00:27:02,500
This is indeed a rare masterpiece.

544
00:27:03,700 --> 00:27:06,900
When egrets fly, they compress their necks to the

545
00:27:07,460 --> 00:27:09,740
point that their lower neck would appear baggy.

546
00:27:10,340 --> 00:27:13,980
I have seen many paintings of egrets by others,

547
00:27:14,260 --> 00:27:16,820
who often make the mistake of putting
in the flying poses of cranes,

548
00:27:17,820 --> 00:27:19,540
with the head, neck and feet

549
00:27:19,740 --> 00:27:22,380
straight into one line.

550
00:27:22,860 --> 00:27:24,660
But Cui Bai has made no such mistake.

551
00:27:25,100 --> 00:27:27,180
One can tell that he has paid attention

552
00:27:27,340 --> 00:27:28,820
to the details of the objects that he is painting.

553
00:27:29,980 --> 00:27:31,660
The other day, you painted Huirou.

554
00:27:32,500 --> 00:27:33,380
It is apparent that

555
00:27:33,380 --> 00:27:35,300
you have not studied with a real painter

556
00:27:35,820 --> 00:27:36,820
and have rather mundane techniques.

557
00:27:37,260 --> 00:27:39,580
However, your painting was quite vivid,

558
00:27:40,060 --> 00:27:41,580
and captured Huirou’s spirit precisely.

559
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:44,260
From then on, I have considered you as an observant

560
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:45,300
and a quite talented painter.

561
00:27:46,980 --> 00:27:48,420
Thank you, Your Highness, for your compliments.

562
00:27:50,260 --> 00:27:54,980
= Dragon Boat Festival =

563
00:28:03,001 --> 00:28:04,779
Zongzi.

564
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:09,340
Madam. Princess.

565
00:28:14,700 --> 00:28:16,620
Have you just returned from the Hall
of Happiness and Tranquility?

566
00:28:16,620 --> 00:28:18,660
What are father and Her Highness’s rewards?

567
00:28:19,260 --> 00:28:20,780
One more roll of silk

568
00:28:20,780 --> 00:28:21,780
than previous years.

569
00:28:21,940 --> 00:28:23,060
Two tiger-head pouches

570
00:28:23,060 --> 00:28:24,220
for Zuixinglai.

571
00:28:24,820 --> 00:28:26,500
Her Highness has also given us

572
00:28:26,500 --> 00:28:27,220
one fragrant pouch each

573
00:28:27,220 --> 00:28:28,740
made of five-colored beads.

574
00:28:28,860 --> 00:28:29,700
Inside were colorful braids

575
00:28:29,700 --> 00:28:31,380
made of gold and silver strands.

576
00:28:31,580 --> 00:28:32,580
Also one painted fan each.

577
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:34,900
What about me?

578
00:28:34,900 --> 00:28:36,860
What about the dried prunes awarded to me
by father?

579
00:28:38,780 --> 00:28:39,580
This is what His Majesty

580
00:28:39,580 --> 00:28:41,180
has rewarded you specifically.

581
00:28:51,580 --> 00:28:52,740
Huaiji is here.

582
00:28:55,100 --> 00:28:56,060
Huaiji, come.

583
00:28:56,700 --> 00:28:58,340
I have things for you.

584
00:29:01,460 --> 00:29:02,260
Go.

585
00:29:05,980 --> 00:29:08,220
I have delivered the paintings of birds
and flowers by Princess

586
00:29:08,340 --> 00:29:10,020
a few days ago to Master Cui.

587
00:29:10,420 --> 00:29:12,380
Master Cui has given some directions
and made a few modifications

588
00:29:12,540 --> 00:29:13,780
and asked me to deliver them to Princess.

589
00:29:15,540 --> 00:29:17,100
His Majesty loves Huirou dearly

590
00:29:18,620 --> 00:29:20,060
and wants her to study painting flowers and birds

591
00:29:20,660 --> 00:29:22,420
but fears that stewardesses
in the palace cannot teach her well.

592
00:29:23,100 --> 00:29:24,020
Therefore, he asked Her Highness to have

593
00:29:24,100 --> 00:29:25,620
the best painter in the palace to teach her.

594
00:29:26,420 --> 00:29:27,940
But Huirou is a girl.

595
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:29,780
Even though she is little,

596
00:29:30,300 --> 00:29:31,900
we cannot let men from outside

597
00:29:31,900 --> 00:29:32,900
teach her in person every day,

598
00:29:33,860 --> 00:29:35,540
so we have to ask you to deliver
the paintings back and forth.

599
00:29:37,460 --> 00:29:38,220
Go

600
00:29:38,420 --> 00:29:40,220
and get the robe I have prepared for Huaiji.

601
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:46,820
I didn’t know what to give you.

602
00:29:47,260 --> 00:29:48,900
I don’t know much about

603
00:29:49,620 --> 00:29:50,500
paintbrushes and inkstones.

604
00:29:51,260 --> 00:29:52,500
The days are getting warmer.

605
00:29:52,500 --> 00:29:53,900
It is time to make new clothes.

606
00:29:54,660 --> 00:29:56,220
I have some top quality thin fabrics

607
00:29:56,580 --> 00:29:59,100
and have asked the Bureau of Clothing
to make two outfits

608
00:29:59,340 --> 00:30:00,500
and one pair of shoes for you.

609
00:30:03,980 --> 00:30:05,620
Thanks to the expectations Her Highness
and His Majesty have

610
00:30:05,740 --> 00:30:07,020
for Princess,

611
00:30:07,380 --> 00:30:08,780
a mere servant like me

612
00:30:08,900 --> 00:30:11,140
could listen to Master Cui talk
about paining in person.

613
00:30:11,700 --> 00:30:13,380
This is a high honor

614
00:30:13,460 --> 00:30:15,020
from His Majesty and Her Highness

615
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:17,540
and good fortune bestowed upon me by Princess.

616
00:30:17,860 --> 00:30:19,700
How dare I receive such a high reward,
Concubine Miao?

617
00:30:22,500 --> 00:30:25,460
You are always so modest and polite.

618
00:30:26,420 --> 00:30:27,540
No wonder His Majesty and Her Highness

619
00:30:27,540 --> 00:30:28,420
like you so much.

620
00:30:29,180 --> 00:30:31,940
I don’t know much about paintings.

621
00:30:32,780 --> 00:30:34,380
Her Highness has mentioned
that you are extremely talented

622
00:30:34,500 --> 00:30:36,500
and that you would be a great aid
to Huirou learning to paint.

623
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:39,380
I was wondering if it was possible

624
00:30:39,900 --> 00:30:41,620
for a girl to end up as a master painter.

625
00:30:41,660 --> 00:30:43,020
Is she really in need of aid?

626
00:30:44,300 --> 00:30:45,900
Huaiji is here to teach me to paint!

627
00:30:46,700 --> 00:30:48,180
I dare not teach Princess.

628
00:30:48,380 --> 00:30:49,620
I was merely relaying Master Cui’s…

629
00:30:49,620 --> 00:30:51,340
Hurry, hurry. There is no time.

630
00:30:56,500 --> 00:30:58,820
Take this. Take this up.

631
00:31:00,940 --> 00:31:03,300
Huaiji, you have to do me a favor.

632
00:31:04,380 --> 00:31:06,340
If you have to do calligraphy work today,

633
00:31:06,820 --> 00:31:08,740
we could paint on another day.

634
00:31:09,260 --> 00:31:10,500
I could head back to my place

635
00:31:10,500 --> 00:31:11,820
and write out everything

636
00:31:12,060 --> 00:31:13,180
that Master Cui

637
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,500
has dictated,

638
00:31:14,500 --> 00:31:15,860
and then relay them to you.

639
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:17,060
It would be clearer that way.

640
00:31:17,460 --> 00:31:20,540
Huaiji, you cannot leave.

641
00:31:21,500 --> 00:31:22,700
Do you know him?

642
00:31:27,260 --> 00:31:28,740
I recognize the calligraphy.

643
00:31:29,020 --> 00:31:31,540
Scholar Ouyang is a leader of the literary circle.

644
00:31:31,820 --> 00:31:32,380
His poems and essays…

645
00:31:32,380 --> 00:31:33,580
I already know about that.

646
00:31:33,580 --> 00:31:35,380
But I don’t know

647
00:31:35,380 --> 00:31:37,100
why he has to write so many

648
00:31:37,100 --> 00:31:39,420
spring festival scrolls that father adores.

649
00:31:39,460 --> 00:31:40,420
What I don’t know even more

650
00:31:40,420 --> 00:31:41,620
is why father asked me

651
00:31:41,620 --> 00:31:42,980
to recite everything.

652
00:31:43,460 --> 00:31:44,940
This shows the love

653
00:31:44,940 --> 00:31:45,900
and high expectations

654
00:31:46,020 --> 00:31:46,980
that His Majesty has for you.

655
00:31:47,380 --> 00:31:48,660
Even you say so.

656
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:49,740
In the past Dragon Boat Festivals,

657
00:31:49,740 --> 00:31:51,940
father would give me

658
00:31:51,940 --> 00:31:52,980
toys that commoners usually play

659
00:31:53,140 --> 00:31:54,140
and also

660
00:31:54,140 --> 00:31:56,300
a full platter of dried prunes.

661
00:31:56,820 --> 00:31:58,420
But this year he said that I am older

662
00:31:58,620 --> 00:31:59,940
that I am a big girl

663
00:32:00,060 --> 00:32:02,380
and that he cannot keep giving me things

664
00:32:02,380 --> 00:32:03,980
that little kids love, like dried fruits.

665
00:32:04,420 --> 00:32:07,100
Even though I am a girl, I am the eldest princess.

666
00:32:07,220 --> 00:32:09,660
I need to be well-versed in literature and senses.

667
00:32:10,060 --> 00:32:11,100
Today is the Dragon Boat Festival.

668
00:32:11,100 --> 00:32:12,820
He gave me the spring festival scrolls

669
00:32:12,980 --> 00:32:14,140
by Scholar Ouyang

670
00:32:14,260 --> 00:32:16,700
so that I could recite and copy them.

671
00:32:17,260 --> 00:32:19,420
Father said that even if I could not recite them,

672
00:32:19,420 --> 00:32:20,740
I should copy them three times

673
00:32:20,740 --> 00:32:23,180
and bring them to the back yard
before I could get to play.

674
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:25,820
Today many royal relatives and family
members of close officials

675
00:32:25,820 --> 00:32:27,940
are invited to stroll about in the back yard.

676
00:32:28,380 --> 00:32:29,940
Zongshi and Miss Gao,

677
00:32:29,940 --> 00:32:32,420
who have been out of the palace
for a few months for home visits,

678
00:32:32,420 --> 00:32:33,620
would also be there today.

679
00:32:33,860 --> 00:32:34,980
By the time I am done with copying
these three times,

680
00:32:34,980 --> 00:32:36,660
it would be noon.

681
00:32:40,140 --> 00:32:41,180
Huaiji,

682
00:32:41,180 --> 00:32:43,500
I know your handwriting is great.

683
00:32:43,660 --> 00:32:46,820
I have heard father and Her Highness praised

684
00:32:47,100 --> 00:32:48,500
that you could imitate

685
00:32:48,500 --> 00:32:50,020
anyone’s handwriting.

686
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:52,900
Even father would not be able to
tell with one glance.

687
00:32:53,380 --> 00:32:55,460
If you could imitate

688
00:32:55,460 --> 00:32:57,100
the great calligraphy

689
00:32:57,100 --> 00:32:58,780
of Scholar Ouyang,

690
00:32:59,300 --> 00:33:02,180
it would be very easy

691
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:04,220
to copy these in my handwriting.

692
00:33:07,620 --> 00:33:08,820
Please.

693
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:11,180
Pretty please.

694
00:33:11,180 --> 00:33:13,260
Just help me out.

695
00:33:48,420 --> 00:33:49,900
This is about the reputation of the court.

696
00:33:49,900 --> 00:33:51,140
We cannot put it off until later.

697
00:34:01,020 --> 00:34:01,940
The imperial censors

698
00:34:01,940 --> 00:34:03,220
have been adamant about the matters
regarding Mr. Xia

699
00:34:03,380 --> 00:34:04,500
and insisted on seeing His Majesty,

700
00:34:04,700 --> 00:34:06,740
saying that it damages the reputation

701
00:34:07,140 --> 00:34:08,740
= Xu Lantiao =
of the court

702
00:34:08,860 --> 00:34:10,580
that the household affairs of an official

703
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:12,300
end up as news

704
00:34:12,380 --> 00:34:13,580
and entertainment on the street.

705
00:34:16,500 --> 00:34:17,300
I see.

706
00:34:17,980 --> 00:34:18,900
You can leave.

707
00:34:52,260 --> 00:34:54,260
Your Majesty.

708
00:35:14,780 --> 00:35:15,700
You adore her.

709
00:35:16,740 --> 00:35:18,460
You spoil her.

710
00:35:19,980 --> 00:35:21,700
And you insisted on holding a wedding banquet.

711
00:35:24,260 --> 00:35:26,380
No wonder that shrew went crazy like this.

712
00:35:26,660 --> 00:35:27,900
You had it coming.

713
00:35:36,340 --> 00:35:36,980
No.

714
00:35:38,700 --> 00:35:40,060
It must be that little bitch

715
00:35:40,540 --> 00:35:41,740
stirring things up behind.

716
00:35:43,660 --> 00:35:44,980
That little bitch.

717
00:35:46,020 --> 00:35:47,700
I will give her a hard time.

718
00:36:03,740 --> 00:36:05,540
Maybe we should send someone to wait
at the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

719
00:36:06,500 --> 00:36:08,020
If they see His Majesty come back to get changed,

720
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:09,740
they’ll escort him to the backyard.

721
00:36:10,140 --> 00:36:10,900
Mother.

722
00:36:10,900 --> 00:36:12,820
I want to wait for father
at the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

723
00:36:13,860 --> 00:36:15,180
You shall accompany Princess

724
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:16,740
to wait at the Hall of Happiness and Tranquility.

725
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:19,540
Go.

726
00:36:19,540 --> 00:36:20,220
Let’s go.

727
00:36:24,860 --> 00:36:26,540
It was said in The Great Learning
in The Book of Rites,

728
00:36:27,180 --> 00:36:29,860
that the ancients who wished to introduce virtues
throughout the world

729
00:36:29,860 --> 00:36:31,260
should first rule their own states well.

730
00:36:31,940 --> 00:36:34,380
Before ruling their states well,
they should first regulate their families.

731
00:36:34,500 --> 00:36:36,780
Before regulating their families,
they should first cultivate themselves.

732
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:39,980
Before cultivating themselves,
they should first train their hearts.

733
00:36:41,180 --> 00:36:43,980
= Cai Xiang, courtesy name Junmo =
Should one regulate his family before rule the state?

734
00:36:45,140 --> 00:36:46,380
The reason why one could not regulate his family

735
00:36:46,580 --> 00:36:48,620
is that he failed to train his heart.

736
00:36:49,060 --> 00:36:50,860
Xia Song is the Chief Executive of Privy Council.

737
00:36:50,900 --> 00:36:52,980
He takes part in state affairs
but could not manage household affairs.

738
00:36:53,260 --> 00:36:54,700
He even ended up having his own wife

739
00:36:54,700 --> 00:36:56,260
suing him for corruption.

740
00:36:57,540 --> 00:36:59,460
It sounds like a drama caused by Mrs. Xia.

741
00:36:59,740 --> 00:37:02,700
But in essence,
it indicates that Xia Song is flawed.

742
00:37:20,180 --> 00:37:21,100
Your Majesty.

743
00:37:23,860 --> 00:37:24,740
Your Majesty.

744
00:37:30,740 --> 00:37:31,660
Your Majesty.

745
00:37:32,340 --> 00:37:35,540
Was I out of the line?

746
00:37:43,180 --> 00:37:44,140
I have heard that

747
00:37:45,260 --> 00:37:47,460
you are known for your beard

748
00:37:47,540 --> 00:37:49,460
and that you are called Lord of Magnificent Beard.

749
00:37:50,620 --> 00:37:52,020
I was curious

750
00:37:54,220 --> 00:37:55,980
if it takes you quite a lot of time

751
00:37:56,340 --> 00:37:58,140
taking care of your beard.

752
00:38:00,420 --> 00:38:02,140
When you go to bed every day,

753
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:05,380
do you keep your beard in your comforter

754
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:07,500
or leave it out?

755
00:38:17,300 --> 00:38:18,860
Since it concerns
the household matters of Xia Song,

756
00:38:19,340 --> 00:38:20,940
why are the imperial censors
bringing it to His Majesty?

757
00:38:22,340 --> 00:38:23,620
No matter how high a post Xia Song holds,

758
00:38:23,740 --> 00:38:25,020
how rampant his household affairs get,

759
00:38:25,380 --> 00:38:27,140
it is not reasonable for the imperial censors

760
00:38:27,580 --> 00:38:28,980
to have His Majesty stay in the Hall of Politics

761
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:30,700
to listen to their discourse

762
00:38:30,940 --> 00:38:32,820
on a state holiday.

763
00:38:36,820 --> 00:38:37,540
Here, catch it.

764
00:38:37,540 --> 00:38:38,180
Pass it to me.

765
00:38:38,180 --> 00:38:39,180
Put it higher. Yes.

766
00:38:39,580 --> 00:38:40,700
His Majesty has arrived.

767
00:38:40,980 --> 00:38:41,780
His Majesty is here.

768
00:38:47,620 --> 00:38:48,100
Father.

769
00:38:48,100 --> 00:38:49,340
Ask Chief Li of Styling to come here.

770
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:52,100
Why do you want your hair combed now, father?

771
00:38:55,140 --> 00:38:57,340
Just now, a few imperial censors

772
00:38:57,340 --> 00:38:59,060
were rambling about classics to me.

773
00:38:59,300 --> 00:39:00,340
I wanted to leave.

774
00:39:00,940 --> 00:39:02,340
So I smiled and told them

775
00:39:02,460 --> 00:39:04,500
that I had understood their rationale

776
00:39:04,580 --> 00:39:05,860
and that we should discuss the matter
after the holiday.

777
00:39:07,020 --> 00:39:08,780
But as soon as I turned my back

778
00:39:08,860 --> 00:39:09,900
and before I could take a step,

779
00:39:09,900 --> 00:39:12,140
Yu Jing caught me by my sleeve and

780
00:39:12,580 --> 00:39:14,860
told me that he had not stated his key argument.

781
00:39:15,060 --> 00:39:17,500
I had to return and listen
until they presented their case.

782
00:39:18,100 --> 00:39:19,420
I didn’t know who it was from,

783
00:39:19,980 --> 00:39:21,660
but there was a heavy smell of body odor
in the room.

784
00:39:22,260 --> 00:39:23,260
It was also quite hot today.

785
00:39:23,620 --> 00:39:25,060
My head was dizzy and my scalp was numb

786
00:39:25,260 --> 00:39:26,260
from the smell and the heat.

787
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:29,100
I have to have my hair combed to freshen up

788
00:39:29,100 --> 00:39:31,020
so that I would look proper for the banquet later.

789
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:48,060
Your Majesty.

790
00:39:48,380 --> 00:39:49,020
Slow down. Slow down.

791
00:39:49,020 --> 00:39:50,420
What did the censors advise on?

792
00:39:51,180 --> 00:39:52,340
What was so important to warrant
such a lengthy advice

793
00:39:52,540 --> 00:39:53,700
that it took them so long to state their case?

794
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:55,540
Nothing.

795
00:39:56,180 --> 00:39:57,220
You don’t need to know.

796
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:00,460
What they said

797
00:40:00,460 --> 00:40:01,740
must be written here.

798
00:40:01,820 --> 00:40:03,380
Could we read it?

799
00:40:03,540 --> 00:40:05,260
- Let me take a look. - Take a look.

800
00:40:05,700 --> 00:40:07,860
Take it easy. Take it easy.

801
00:40:08,020 --> 00:40:09,780
Don’t damage it. Take it easy.

802
00:40:10,460 --> 00:40:11,980
We’ll have Princess read it.

803
00:40:17,380 --> 00:40:25,140
I have heard that Your Majesty
have considered the fact that the number of

804
00:40:25,460 --> 00:40:28,140
natural disasters have declined…

805
00:40:28,820 --> 00:40:30,900
Father. I do not know this word.

806
00:40:35,540 --> 00:40:38,500
They said that there has been heavy rainfall
this year

807
00:40:38,540 --> 00:40:40,340
and that there have been earthquakes recently.

808
00:40:40,780 --> 00:40:42,020
This is due to the excess of women.

809
00:40:43,060 --> 00:40:45,540
They hoped that useless personnel

810
00:40:45,980 --> 00:40:47,020
can be removed from the palace.

811
00:40:49,380 --> 00:40:52,060
Father, what are useless personnel?

812
00:40:55,380 --> 00:40:57,180
Why don’t Your Majesty get rid of

813
00:40:57,180 --> 00:40:58,220
some of those officials who like to talk nonsense,

814
00:40:58,380 --> 00:40:59,660
so you can get a moment of peace?

815
00:40:59,980 --> 00:41:01,780
Why tolerate their rambling?

816
00:41:02,980 --> 00:41:04,100
Nowadays, people in the capital

817
00:41:04,620 --> 00:41:06,260
are accumulating more and more wealth

818
00:41:06,500 --> 00:41:07,820
thanks to the blessing from Your Majesty.

819
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:10,060
With money in their hands

820
00:41:10,740 --> 00:41:12,460
who doesn’t want to have a few concubines?

821
00:41:13,060 --> 00:41:14,700
= Chief Li of Styling =
Emperor has concubines,

822
00:41:15,140 --> 00:41:16,140
but officials have no right

823
00:41:16,140 --> 00:41:17,260
to judge that.

824
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:22,740
Apart from rich merchants,

825
00:41:22,940 --> 00:41:24,420
many high-ranking officials

826
00:41:24,580 --> 00:41:27,020
have singers and dancers in their households.

827
00:41:27,860 --> 00:41:29,340
For those who are in favor,

828
00:41:29,340 --> 00:41:30,900
they cannot wait to fill their houses with women.

829
00:41:31,860 --> 00:41:33,380
Ouyang Xiu and Song Qi

830
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:34,660
are among the people

831
00:41:34,660 --> 00:41:35,820
who like to talk nonsense to Your Majesty the most.

832
00:41:36,620 --> 00:41:38,660
They talk about classics in court,

833
00:41:39,060 --> 00:41:40,820
but conduct raunchy business in private.

834
00:41:42,020 --> 00:41:43,180
When they found

835
00:41:43,420 --> 00:41:45,060
singers at the banquet attractive,

836
00:41:45,500 --> 00:41:47,020
they would write poems

837
00:41:47,820 --> 00:41:49,860
and the host would give them the girls.

838
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,580
In the end,

839
00:41:51,580 --> 00:41:53,180
it would become lovely
stories of a scholar and a beautiful lady.

840
00:41:53,820 --> 00:41:55,020
But when it comes to Your Majesty,

841
00:41:55,380 --> 00:41:57,140
they’re accusing you of having too many women.

842
00:41:57,980 --> 00:41:59,660
But these scholars and officials

843
00:41:59,660 --> 00:42:00,660
end up enjoying their lives to the fullest.

844
00:42:02,420 --> 00:42:04,380
How come you know the private business

845
00:42:05,140 --> 00:42:06,380
of officials at the court?

846
00:42:07,660 --> 00:42:09,500
People in the palace also talk about these things.

847
00:42:12,260 --> 00:42:13,300
Are Your Majesty really going to

848
00:42:13,300 --> 00:42:14,180
take their advice?

849
00:42:17,580 --> 00:42:19,940
If the censors have a point

850
00:42:19,940 --> 00:42:20,940
and are applicable to the situation,

851
00:42:21,260 --> 00:42:22,420
I shall follow their advice.

852
00:42:25,780 --> 00:42:27,700
Then, if reduction needs to be made on personnel,

853
00:42:28,380 --> 00:42:29,860
then start from me first.

854
00:42:31,500 --> 00:42:33,300
I thought what the censors said

855
00:42:34,660 --> 00:42:36,140
was often a bit over the top

856
00:42:36,860 --> 00:42:38,380
and were cautionary at best.

857
00:42:40,300 --> 00:42:42,020
Never had I imagined that what they said

858
00:42:43,060 --> 00:42:44,380
could be right to the point.

859
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:51,060
Ask the Imperial Recorder to bring
the Palace Book to the backyard.

860
00:42:58,220 --> 00:43:07,900
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

861
00:43:09,220 --> 00:43:17,580
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

862
00:43:20,420 --> 00:43:25,140
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

863
00:43:26,100 --> 00:43:30,260
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

864
00:43:31,700 --> 00:43:37,180
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

865
00:43:37,180 --> 00:43:41,980
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

866
00:43:45,660 --> 00:43:51,300
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

867
