00:44:35,820 --> 00:44:40,460
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

876
00:44:41,500 --> 00:44:46,660
♪ The howling wind ♪

877
00:44:47,020 --> 00:44:51,100
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

878
